    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-103">在.NET Framework 2.0 版中，<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>派生自新<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-103">In the .NET Framework version 2.0, <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> derives from the new <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-104">一个<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>功能上等效于<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle>使用创建<xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.ManualReset?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-104">A <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> is functionally equivalent to an <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> created with <xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.ManualReset?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="93256-105">与不同<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>类，<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle>类提供了对访问已命名系统同步事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-105">Unlike the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> class, the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class provides access to named system synchronization events.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-106"><xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> 允许线程能够相互通信通过发出信号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-106"><xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> allows threads to communicate with each other by signaling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-107">通常情况下，此通信涉及其他线程可以继续操作之前，必须完成的一个线程的任务。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-107">Typically, this communication concerns a task which one thread must complete before other threads can proceed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-108">开始之前其他必须完成的活动线程时线程继续执行，它将调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A>放置`ManualResetEvent`处于非信号状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-108">When a thread begins an activity that must complete before other threads proceed, it calls <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A> to put `ManualResetEvent` in the non-signaled state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-109">此线程可以认为的控制`ManualResetEvent`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-109">This thread can be thought of as controlling the `ManualResetEvent`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-110">线程调用<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>上`ManualResetEvent`将阻止，正在等待信号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-110">Threads that call <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> on the `ManualResetEvent` will block, awaiting the signal.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-111">当控制线程完成活动时，它将调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A>发出信号等待线程可以继续执行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-111">When the controlling thread completes the activity, it calls <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> to signal that the waiting threads can proceed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-112">将释放所有等待的线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-112">All waiting threads are released.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-113">一旦它被终止，`ManualResetEvent`手动重置前保持终止状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-113">Once it has been signaled, `ManualResetEvent` remains signaled until it is manually reset.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-114">也就是说，调用`WaitOne`立即返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-114">That is, calls to `WaitOne` return immediately.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-115">您可以控制的初始状态`ManualResetEvent`通过将一个布尔值传递给构造函数中，`true`如果信号的初始状态和`false`否则为。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-115">You can control the initial state of a `ManualResetEvent` by passing a Boolean value to the constructor, `true` if the initial state is signaled and `false` otherwise.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-116">`ManualResetEvent` 也可以用于`static`<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A>和<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-116">`ManualResetEvent` can also be used with the `static`<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A> and <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-117">有关线程同步机制的详细信息，请参阅[ManualResetEvent 和 ManualResetEventSlim](~/docs/standard/threading/manualresetevent-and-manualreseteventslim.md)概念性文档中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-117">For more information about thread synchronization mechanisms, see [ManualResetEvent and ManualResetEventSlim](~/docs/standard/threading/manualresetevent-and-manualreseteventslim.md) in the conceptual documentation.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-118">下面的示例演示如何<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>工作原理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-118">The following example demonstrates how <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> works.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-119">该示例启动与<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>中未终止的状态 (即，`false`传递给构造函数)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-119">The example starts with a <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> in the unsignaled state (that is, `false` is passed to the constructor).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-120">此示例将创建三个线程时，每个哪些块上<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>通过调用其<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-120">The example creates three threads, each of which blocks on the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> by calling its <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-121">当用户按**Enter**键，此示例调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A>方法中，会释放所有三个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-121">When the user presses the **Enter** key, the example calls the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> method, which releases all three threads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-122">与此相反的行为<xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>类，该类在每次发布后自动重置一次释放一个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-122">Contrast this with the behavior of the <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> class, which releases threads one at a time, resetting automatically after each release.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-123">按下**Enter**密钥再次演示<xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>处于终止状态，直到其<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A>调用方法： 此示例将启动这两个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-123">Pressing the **Enter** key again demonstrates that the <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> remains in the signaled state until its <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A> method is called: The example starts two more threads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-124">当它们调用时不会阻止这些线程<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>方法，但改为运行到完成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-124">These threads do not block when they call the <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> method, but instead run to completion.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="93256-125">按下**Enter**密钥再次使该示例调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A>方法，并启动一个阻止调用时的多个线程<xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-125">Pressing the **Enter** key again causes the example to call the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Reset%2A> method and to start one more thread, which blocks when it calls <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93256-126">按下**Enter**密钥一个最后一次调用<xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A>释放最后一个线程和该程序结束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93256-126">Pressing the **Enter** key one final time calls <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> to release the last thread, and the program ends.</span></span>  
  
